# UI components

> Source canonique : `.agents/ui-components.md`

**Prefer `adabraka-ui` components over hand-rolled `div`s.** Only build a
custom widget when adabraka-ui genuinely has no equivalent.

## Must-do

1. **Search adabraka first** — `patches/adabraka-ui/` (`Dialog`, `Sheet`,
   `Select`, `Combobox`, `PopoverMenu`, `ConfirmDialog`, …).
2. **Centered modals / forms** → **`Dialog`**, not new `*-form-overlay` stacks.
3. **Connection / server pickers** → **`Select` / `Combobox`** (see
   `connection_combobox.rs`).
4. Hand-roll only as exception — one-line comment *why* + link to backlog item.

## Modals (critical)

Do **not** ship `absolute()` backdrop + centered `div` without `max_h` + scroll
body. Footer buttons get clipped (incident: `script_form` "New Script").

Target: `adabraka_ui::overlays::dialog::Dialog` (`max_h` ~85vh built-in).
Interim legacy pattern: `.agents/overflow.md` § Centered modals.

## Backlog highlights

| Area | Target |
|------|--------|
| Form modals (script, port forward, login, …) | `Dialog` |
| Side panels | `Sheet` |
